kissmig 2.0-1
-------------
* BUG-FIX: overpredictions with binary suitability since v2.0-0
* 'n_random' default increased to 100,000 to reduce regular patterns

kissmig 2.0-0
-------------
* BREAKING CHANGES: migration from raster to terra
* NEW: parallel processing for 'kissmig::kissmig()' through optional argument 'n_threads'
* general performance improvements

kissmig 1.0-4
-------------
* minor revision according to CRAN check status

kissmig 1.0-3
-------------
* minor changes of documentation
* first version available on CRAN

kissmig 1.0-2
-------------
* minor changes of documentation

kissmig 1.0-1
-------------
* first version published on the kissmig homepage

kissmig 1.0-0
-------------
* initial private release available for expert opinion on Nobis & Normand (2014)
